@startuml REQ-0062 Certificate Provisioning
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 200
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

box "System" #LightBlue
  participant "Cert Manager" as Cert_Manager
  participant "Provisioning Manager" as Provisioning_Manager
  participant "Comm Manager" as Comm_Manager
end box

header
  **REQ-0062: Certificate Provisioning**
  //Description:// Fetch and install device certificate from provisioning\nserver.
  //Acceptance Criteria:// Certificate downloaded via HTTPS and written to flash.
end header


Cert_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_CERT_INSTALLED\nCert_Provision() -> Provision_OnCertInstalled()
note right of Provisioning_Manager: PROV_STATE_READY
Provisioning_Manager -> Comm_Manager: Comm_SendStatus()
activate Comm_Manager
Comm_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: return
deactivate Comm_Manager
Provisioning_Manager --> Provisioning_Manager: EVENT:PROV_COMPLETE

@enduml